{"tid":1175321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又缺席！台灣萬安演習南部總指揮韓國瑜缺席 由副市長代打　他怒轟：韓國瑜沒軍紀","createTime":"2019-05-28T12:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T00:39:03.000Z","uid":35790,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"20ecf1949cbdb3a693599adc684af3599cff0ddd","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"又缺席！萬安演習由副市長代打　他怒轟：韓國瑜沒軍紀<br />\n<br />\n2019/05/28<br />\n<br />\n南部萬安42號演習響警報今(28日)下午登場，不過高雄市總指揮官韓國瑜市長缺席未到場，改由副市長洪東煒代打。臉書「打馬悍將粉絲團」立即連發兩文痛批韓國瑜之前嘲諷國軍沒軍法，「事實證明，最沒軍紀的，就是韓國瑜自己」，還問「這人真的有在上班嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n萬安42號演習今天下午輪到南部地區(台南市、高雄市、屏東縣、金門縣)，但高雄市總指揮韓國瑜市長並未到場坐鎮，改由副市長洪東煒指揮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這是韓國瑜第一次擔任總指揮，但就因故缺席了。昨天台北市萬安演習柯文哲市長不但在應變中心聽取簡報，更冒雨觀看搶救實兵演練、高空作業車救援演、練繩索救援演練等。</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜的缺席，讓網友看不下去，臉書社團「打馬悍將團」立即發文批判，指「韓導又不見了，這人真的有在上班嗎」，<span style=\"color: red;\">還將韓國瑜在美國嘲諷「國軍沒軍法像穿西裝的太監」採訪畫面，製圖對照今日的缺席，痛批韓國瑜「最沒軍紀的，就是韓國瑜自己」。</span><br />\n<br />\n網友也在下方紛紛留言，「高雄本來就沒有市長」，「懂什麼，這才叫真的演習，韓導真的打仗一定不會在位置上呀」。高雄市政府目前尚未說明韓國瑜未能到場坐鎮指揮的原因。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/1140133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fpolitics%2F1140133&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2ARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=23688e97\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/1140133</a>"},{"pid":"c22696bf16fc708b183269febf0adb07b85dc3f3","tid":1175321,"uid":43428,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"投左件垃圾出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a98086e0bfdf1abff559b460703803c559bf3a0","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"俾佢做咗總統<br />\n如果台海開戰<br />\n會唔會龜縮？<br />\n台灣人好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79ccab07afa0f43bcade371ba98de3cf374ac8a","tid":1175321,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e21cb982773023ff8c30fb896900875f534c39","tid":1175321,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"你叫黃毓民點奶呀？<br />\n<br />\n炒車架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f8d7ed10e76b54221c8487c2a55e36fb6ae02e","tid":1175321,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"賣國瑜 : 我諗緊點cap水發大財呀 軍演咪搞我"},{"pid":"735ab34f8dc20fa3703381ce0682280a4e2a9146","tid":1175321,"uid":41116,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctCsPjk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctCsPjk.png&h=7f37604b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"842a35f1a5c3b39db3afe2a6d1c8690d375893b9","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"萬安演習不見韓國瑜？高閔琳：中共打來保證第一個落跑<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-28 <br />\n<br />\n〔記者王榮祥／高雄報導〕萬安演習卻不見指揮官？民進黨高市議員高閔琳今表示，<br />\n<br />\n全中運落跑先走，萬安演習更直接缺席，看來「落跑市長」恐怕是勢在必行了，她問市長韓國瑜，您這樣當市長會不會太過份！<br />\n<br />\n高閔琳說，韓國瑜本身是陸官出身，先前批評我國軍像太監，現在是已正面表態要選總統、三軍統帥的人，竟缺席視同作戰的萬安演習！<br />\n<br />\n她認為，韓國瑜是支持九二假共識、一個中國、一國兩制的人，到底還有什麼臉講「守護中華民國」！有什麼臉講對「中華民國的命運及未來走向充滿焦慮」，什麼2020總統大選是中華民國的生死存亡之戰」！<br />\n<br />\n高閔琳痛批這種「騙子嘴臉，實在太噁心！中共打來、韓國瑜保證第一個先招降落跑！誰理你們高雄人、台灣人呀！大家醒醒吧」！<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;<br />\n<br />\n韓三桂"},{"pid":"61d407f731fd101901d34d79dc66d39c8d1ff0c3","tid":1175321,"uid":253836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"共軍真係打到去台灣，韓國瑜第一個幫共軍帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b883a5fd2a53f30111ebfa8d724b0e443510e0c","tid":1175321,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"61d407f731fd101901d34d79dc66d39c8d1ff0c3","tid":1175321,"uid":253836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"共軍真係打到去台灣，韓國瑜第一個幫共軍帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"所以個演習都好真<br />\n<br />\n演習應該基於真正出現既情況"},{"pid":"b98f4bd19cca43dbc5bbb01b059bddca35399c32","tid":1175321,"uid":231927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72aaa5dabfae85eb04651993efe65037ab337fa6","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=v_jO9bKUmrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv_jO9bKUmrs&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2ARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b5e38dc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=v_jO9bKUmrs</a><br />\n萬安演習遇大雨　柯文哲視察讚同仁辛苦了"},{"pid":"24bfcff86978899a813aadccbbf252d72b880fd1","tid":1175321,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<br />\n韓國魚稱帝萬歲"},{"pid":"d87bb1289f62b1b71b6d344993745e5aad0583dd","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"可能去咗加拿大探兩個愛女"},{"pid":"786868da6b6c48046b48b4a67c3bba7d831e12d8","tid":1175321,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"去左發大財"},{"pid":"adf53e4745508b1dd0381d428085c2cdf8fd6c13","tid":1175321,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"786868da6b6c48046b48b4a67c3bba7d831e12d8","tid":1175321,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"去左發大財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"去咗帶路"},{"pid":"2ce4207acafb8d28e25be3a225938131b6dbba24"